@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ffveyp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.94 - tmp + 0.23)) / wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.13)))
    v0 = v1
    v0 = ((0.33 + (tmp + 0.32 / tmp + 0.55)) + wp.abs(0.67))
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v0 + 0.17) / (v2 + 0.81 + v0 + 0.45)))
    data[tid] = v0
